Terdapat simbol untuk membayar bonus di mana-mana sahaja pada skrin. Jumlah bilangan simbol yang sama pada skrin pada akhir putaran menentukan nilai bonus.
Ini ialah simbol SCATTER.
Tanda SCATTER muncul pada semua gulungan.
SCATTER mempunyai bonus pembayaran di mana-mana lokasi.
Jumlah pertaruhan ialah 100 kali jumlah pertaruhan setiap baris.
Ciri-ciri Tumbling

Fungsi rollover bermakna selepas setiap putaran, kombinasi yang menang akan dibayar dan semua simbol yang menang akan hilang. Simbol yang tinggal akan jatuh ke bahagian bawah skrin, dan ruang kosong akan digantikan dengan simbol dari atas.
Selepas semua rollover yang dihasilkan oleh putaran asas selesai, semua bonus akan ditambah kepada baki pemain.
Ini adalah simbol pengganda. Mereka muncul pada semua aci, dan dalam permainan asas dan putaran percuma, mereka mungkin muncul secara rawak semasa putaran dan guling.
Setiap kali simbol pengganda muncul, ia mendapat nilai pengganda secara rawak, dari 2 kali hingga 2000 kali.
Apabila urutan rollover tamat, nilai semua simbol pengganda pada skrin akan ditambah dan jumlah bonus urutan akan didarab dengan nilai akhir.
Peraturan Spin Percuma
Dapatkan fungsi putaran percuma apabila 4 atau lebih simbol SCATTER muncul di mana-mana sahaja pada skrin.
Pusingan bermula dengan 15 putaran percuma.

Dalam pusingan putaran percuma, setiap kali simbol pengganda muncul dan membawa kepada kemenangan, nilai pengganda ditambah kepada jumlah pengganda. Sepanjang pusingan, setiap kali sebarang simbol pengganda baru muncul dan membawa kepada kemenangan, jumlah nilai pengganda juga digunakan untuk mendarab jumlah kemenangan. Dalam pusingan putaran percuma, 5 putaran percuma tambahan akan diberi ganjaran setiap kali 3 atau lebih simbol SCATTER muncul. Aci khas digunakan dalam pusingan putaran percuma.
Nota Depan

Gandaan pertaruhan 25x - peluang untuk memenangi putaran percuma secara semula jadi berganda. Lebih banyak simbol SCATTER muncul pada aci. Ciri pembelian putaran percuma dinyahdayakan. Pertaruhan gandaan 20x - Bayar jumlah yang bersamaan dengan 100 kali jumlah pertaruhan untuk membeli pusingan putaran percuma.
Beli Spins Percuma

Hanya beli pada 100 kali jumlah pertaruhan semasa anda untuk mencetuskan pusingan putaran percuma serta-merta daripada permainan asas. Selepas ciri 25x pertaruhan hadapan didayakan, pembelian ciri putaran percuma akan dilumpuhkan.

Bonus putaran percuma diberikan kepada pemain selepas pusingan.
Spins percuma jumlah bonus dalam sejarah mengandungi bonus untuk keseluruhan kitaran.

values: PAYS
Symbols pay anywhere on the screen. The total number of the same symbol on the screen at the end of a spin determines the value of the win.
This is the SCATTER symbol.
SCATTER symbol is present on all reels.
SCATTER pays on any position.
Total Bet is 100x Bet Per Line.
TUMBLE FEATURE

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with symbols coming from above.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
These are the multiplier symbols. They are present on all reels and can hit randomly during spins and tumbles in both base game and FREE SPINS.
Whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 2000x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the values of all MULTIPLIER symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
FREE SPINS RULES
The FREE SPINS FEATURE is awarded when 4 or more SCATTER symbols hit anywhere on the screen.
The round starts with 15 free spins.

During the FREE SPINS round, whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits and the spin results in a win, the MULTIPLIER value gets added to the total multiplier. For the whole duration of the round, whenever any new MULTIPLIER symbol hits and results in a win the total multiplier value is also used to multiply the win. Whenever 3 or more SCATTER symbols hit during the FREE SPINS ROUND, 5 additional free spins are awarded. Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
ANTE BET
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently.

The possible values are
Bet multiplier 25x - the chance to win free spins naturally is doubled. More SCATTER symbols are present on the reels. The FREE SPINS PURCHASE FEATURE is disabled. Bet multiplier 20x - gives the ability to purchase a FREE SPINS ROUND by paying a value equal to 100x total bet.
BUY FREE SPINS
The FREE SPINS ROUND can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet. When the 25x ante bet feature is enabled, the BUY FREE SPINS feature is disabled.
GAME RULES
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
Symbols pay anywhere.
All wins are multiplied by base bet.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
When winning with multiple symbols, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

A funo de rolagem significa que, aps cada rotao, a combinao vencedora  paga e todos os smbolos vencedores desaparecem. Os smbolos restantes caem na parte inferior da tela e os espaos vazios so substitudos por smbolos de cima.

Symbols pay anywhere on the screen. The total number of the same symbol on the screen at the end of a spin determines the value of the win.

All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
These are the multiplier symbols. They are present on all reels and can hit randomly during spins and tumbles in both base game and FREE SPINS.
Whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 500x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the values of all MULTIPLIER symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
The FREE SPINS FEATURE is awarded when 4 or more SCATTER symbols hit anywhere on the screen.
The round starts with 15 free spins.
